value.text:
I'm angry,
says he

as he roams the streets,
masked,
with his gun or his knife or his bat or his fists;
his weapon drawn;
tells the businesses to close,
the streets to shut;
burns down the houses,
drags brown children into the street;
beats his wife.

I'm angry about these violent men,
says he
